Another “golden feather” in Pakistan’s cap.

@ForeignOfficePk, can you clarify where TRF operates from? 

TRF is another front of Lashkar-e-Taiba. LeT has been designated a terrorist organisation for years. Last year, its proxy wing TRF was also officially designated as a terrorist organisation.

